{"tid":948950,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【交換禮物】一人放低一個遺憾，我幫你修正佢","createTime":"2018-12-20T12:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T18:28:24.000Z","uid":8820,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"29cdf28ea732644149a6d9ab0f093bcac6b16e67","tid":948950,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:38:32.000Z","msg":"有啲遺憾可能唔算好大件事，但係你會記成世，好想知道如果當時無咁做結果會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似我唔見咗細個喺跑online識嘅網友電話，只係記得佢住邊區，一直好想搵返佢 睇吓佢過成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟兩年前喺講故台寫過一個幫人修正遺憾嘅故事<br />\n今年聖誕就想搞個「遺憾收集箱」，收集大家嘅遺憾，我用局外人嘅身份幫你續寫落去：如果當時你做另一個決定，平行時空嘅你又會過成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如你嘅遺憾係無鼓起勇氣同女神表白<br />\n想修正嘅決定係：畢業禮last day抄佢牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n修正之後，可能你嘅結局會係成功做到女神嘅兵，但最後反而因為一次想逞英雄保護佢而撞車終身殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「遺憾收集箱」</div><br />\n1）將你嘅遺憾寄去遺憾收集箱  <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2AaFs0D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2AaFs0D&d=0pJ34ZEMQy7P7%2FdOqtSk726kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7b6aba35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2AaFs0D</a><br />\n2）我幫你續寫修正後嘅故事結局，寄返email畀你，順便講聲聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n＊期間限定：即日至12月31日<br />\n<br />\n內容得我一個會睇到，唔使擔心會被相認嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （除非你想公開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ） <br />\n 希望有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28eafc127fba67e430ab7b3739477002909490d","tid":948950,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:39:12.000Z","msg":"新故？"},{"pid":"8df32f0b2581208cb1a313b182d271bf3aecd84d","tid":948950,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"初戀係處 依家果個唔係處"},{"pid":"6b0fa45f8153faf7e8b5d6d9807ee8c609337db1","tid":948950,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea04aab95cce0695f93004c52bc39c6bd84619cf","tid":948950,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b28eafc127fba67e430ab7b3739477002909490d","tid":948950,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:39:12.000Z","msg":"新故？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:45:56.000Z","msg":"唔係故嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係想收集大家嘅真實遺憾，續寫故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0fa20d191c8fe8e3bf89092757ca5839a5fa2d","tid":948950,"uid":8820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8df32f0b2581208cb1a313b182d271bf3aecd84d","tid":948950,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"初戀係處 依家果個唔係處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"修正：無同初戀分手，咁你而家嘅女朋友咪係處囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b7cdfcf5a5084294176c45a064481bdf73b661","tid":948950,"uid":8820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6b0fa45f8153faf7e8b5d6d9807ee8c609337db1","tid":948950,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"修正：生於北京，冬天可以睇雪，但春夏秋都食霧霾，最後頂唔順拎單程證落嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed734a03cb7c70c5e9cd357c349fd41699833ed4","tid":948950,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/20/205133_41cfbdedbabdce109d3343725efa385a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F20%2F205133_41cfbdedbabdce109d3343725efa385a.png&h=7abcdbc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c865d16f5b0d5ce3a1f763898c57ea4da70fc60","tid":948950,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed734a03cb7c70c5e9cd357c349fd41699833ed4","tid":948950,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/20/205133_41cfbdedbabdce109d3343725efa385a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F20%2F205133_41cfbdedbabdce109d3343725efa385a.png&h=7abcdbc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  預祝巴打聖誕快樂，接下來嘅人生都無遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42098cefdda8225f356ed632bcddd909c6f5057f","tid":948950,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"個箱已經接到三位巴打／絲打嘅遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投稿去google form嘅我email會覆得長啲，真係寫返個故事畀你<br />\n如果想短短哋玩下就留言回覆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d041759c262198c7a0818affb231e8acbd3ae7","tid":948950,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3307bb6b78f2b6cd5be1699360e6c9df70e5d26","tid":948950,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:47:46.000Z","msg":"中學冇拍拖<br />\n完"},{"pid":"a96480c86bf4b6aabae8184726760e0550ded006","tid":948950,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d041759c262198c7a0818affb231e8acbd3ae7","tid":948950,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep